      <h2 class="about-heading">Chimes with Friends</h2>
      <p class="about-body">Daily Practice is built around a simple concept of chimes. A chime is a sonic signature unique to you and everyone else in Daily Practice. Anytime someone practices, you get to hear their chime. You can even enable real-time chimes while you practice, making the experience feel more communal and supportive. Coming soon — send chimes as voice notes for even more mutual support.</p>
